sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as User
  participant C as ClientA / ClientB
  participant SSO as SSO Server
  participant R as Redis

  U->>C: Click Logout (this device)
  C->>SSO: POST /logout (Bearer access_token)

  SSO->>SSO: verifySession(access_token)
  SSO->>R: GET session:{sessionId}
  SSO->>R: SCARD userSessions:{userId}

  SSO->>R: GET session:{sessionId} (for cleanup context)
  SSO->>R: DEL session:{sessionId}
  SSO->>R: SREM userSessions:{userId} sessionId
  alt session has device binding
    SSO->>R: DEL deviceSession:{deviceType}:{deviceId}
  end

  SSO-->>C: 200 {message: "logout success"}
  C->>C: Destroy local session/cookies

  C->>SSO: GET /session-info (old access_token)
  SSO-->>C: 401 Session not found / Unauthorized